title: SHANY 2012 Edition All In One Harmony Makeup Kit, 25 Ounce
description: This functional palette is perfect for the makeup artist in you. With 168 highly pigmented eye shadows it will be easy to go from day to night. title: SHANY Cosmetics Feather Hair Extension Kit, 8 Ounce (Feather Hair, Hook, Beads, Feather Grizzly Solid Mix All-In-One) -100 Piece
description: 100 piece Shany feather hair extension. Shampoo it, iron it, and even cut it. Synthetic feather extension. Complete kit that brings you all you need to get the job done.
